#: activity/activity.info:2
msgid "Memorize"
msgstr "დამახსოვრება"

#: activity/activity.info:3
msgid ""
"Here you can play games that challenge your memory! But, more importantly, "
"you can create your own game to test the memory of others!"
msgstr ""

#: activity/activity.info:4
msgid ""
"Memorize is about finding matching pairs. A pair can be images, sounds and "
"text and this could be extended to animations or movie snippets as well. "
"Which pairs match is up to the creator of the game. Memorize is more than a "
"predefined game you can play, it allows you to create new games yourself as "
"well."
msgstr ""

